# Diary

Repo-local session capture for this L1 template repository.

## Rule

Use `./diary/` as the canonical raw log for work in this repository.

- Entry: `YYYY-MM-DD.md`
- Multiple sessions/day: `YYYY-MM-DD-2.md`
- Crystallize to: `tips/` and `docs/learnings/` when patterns generalize

## Entry template

```markdown
# YYYY-MM-DD — [Session Focus]

## What I Did
- [Actions]

## What Surprised Me
- [Unexpected outcomes]

## Patterns
- [Repeated structures]

## Crystallization Candidates
- → docs/learnings/
- → tips/meta/
```
